{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Automatically manages a cue bus for monitoring soloed tracks in REAPER. Creates MASTER and CUE tracks if they don't exist, sets MASTER track to solo-defeat mode, optimized for CPU usage with adaptive polling frequency, efficient track searching, and state-change detection. Prevents user from manually soloing MASTER and CUE tracks.\par}
}

